{"tid":1191201,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［認真］大家好應該趁仲有得救嘅時候 做啲嘢","createTime":"2019-06-07T19:35:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T10:25:49.000Z","uid":111225,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c2bd5110058e7b76a4148f5e5449fdcac209b7b4","tid":1191201,"uid":111225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T19:35:30.000Z","msg":"睇完隔離post 乜q 666段片真係好心淡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n眾所周知 呢十年國內太多新移民 太多內地文化湧入香港<br />\n呢個post唔係阻止大家去汲取中國/普通話文化<br />\n（先利申 冇睇任何內地綜藝節目/合拍節目）<br />\n但係接收其他文化嘅同時 作為香港人嘅你唔應該忘本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要支持香港獨有嘅文化 過去咁多年嘅傳統<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係嘅話 再過多十年 廣東話文化會開始淡化<br />\n我唔想第時基本法上面寫香港有3個官方語言：<br />\n普通話 英語 最後先係廣東話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先 大家自己應該以身作則 <br />\n廣東話有好多盞鬼嘅地方 用多啲！<br />\n得香港同澳門係官方語言 我地要將優良傳統延長落去<br />\n繁體字先表達最想表達嘅意思 用多啲！<br />\n以前中學都覺得簡體字好似方便啲<br />\n（屌 其實咪又係快撚左嗰一秒）<br />\n識女仔識返啲有近代香港血統 溝多啲！<br />\n等啲唔肯融入嘅內地人冇人要返去搵食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n還我香港 唔好睇少自己嘅力量<br />\n只要我哋加加埋埋 力量一啲都唔細<br />\n香港其實真係一個福地<br />\n為自己 為我哋下一代緊守我哋嘅崗位<br />\n好嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"947c922114ddc8dda7095f1f03f0996432495d9d","tid":1191201,"uid":111225,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T19:40:51.000Z","msg":"如果有機會接觸下一代嘅大家（教畜/補習等）<br />\n要鼓勵多啲下一代講廣東話 用繁體字<br />\n唔識教到佢識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c2caec4bdbfd58f8c4f95e2f785a802e4f0d60a","tid":1191201,"uid":137059,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T19:47:37.000Z","msg":"中學讀通識寫繁體寫撚到手殘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔識寫亦唔想學寫殘體字"},{"pid":"8c61ed79d12c698ef39e1cd1738353f24609682e","tid":1191201,"uid":111225,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T19:48:24.000Z","msg":"唔好俾咁多機會國內商家<br />\n佢整少少野出嚟 你表示少許支持<br />\n佢哋就會根據大家嘅支持 <br />\n繼續搞更多更多嘅嘢 進一步侵蝕我哋嘅文化<br />\n循環嚟"},{"pid":"d6f8c2bc4590400cf37ab65426a88479468e6677","tid":1191201,"uid":111225,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c2caec4bdbfd58f8c4f95e2f785a802e4f0d60a","tid":1191201,"uid":137059,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T19:47:37.000Z","msg":"中學讀通識寫繁體寫撚到手殘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔識寫亦唔想學寫殘體字"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T19:50:33.000Z","msg":"Ching好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n宜家就算趕時間 去到最後一秒<br />\n我都唔會寫簡體字 <br />\n寧願寫唔曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b311ec04a08f21325372763941e81483d69cc7c9","tid":1191201,"uid":45368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T20:29:49.000Z","msg":"5p 字夠係本土文化啦<br />\n連登仔幾時有專重過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咪又係喊打喊殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"096a8fda8795405b869c93c2ad758b3b1366ced3","tid":1191201,"uid":46356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T02:33:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇完隔離post 乜q 666段片真係好心淡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n乜o野來的?"},{"pid":"4d247db7a049e0ac74709f268b8360ac8600d572","tid":1191201,"uid":111225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"096a8fda8795405b869c93c2ad758b3b1366ced3","tid":1191201,"uid":46356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T02:33:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇完隔離post 乜q 666段片真係好心淡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n乜o野來的?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T06:11:35.000Z","msg":"「牛逼」「網紅」等內地用語入侵香港？已經無人講「犀利」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1189746\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/118974